A sprawling workshop table viewed from above in Studio Ghibli style, covered with dozens of colorful mechanical puzzle pieces and modular components in various stages of assembly. Tiny enchanted tools float nearby - tweezers, magnifying glasses, and delicate brushes. Each component piece has a distinct whimsical design - some with gears, others with flowing organic shapes, crystals, or miniature screens showing abstract patterns. Warm afternoon light streams through a large arched window, casting golden rays across the organized chaos. Small dust motes dance in the light. The color palette features soft teals, warm oranges, cream whites, and deep purples. The scene conveys the joy of building and combining many specialized parts into something greater.
